  "detailed_description": "Straya is an Action based First Person Shooter set in Australia around the late 1960's. With a focus on surviving the many dangerous animals that inhabit the land, air and water, the player can perform jobs, hunt, collect and roam freely in an open world.<br />\r\n<br />\r\nTravel by foot, horse, chopper and boats.<br />\r\nCollect bush tucker to craft elixers.<br />\r\nUse the metal detector to find valuables and avoid land mines.<br />\r\nPan for gold and fish in the creeks and rivers.<br />\r\nGet access to special items by performing jobs and discovering locations.<br />\r\nExperience elements based on the Dreamtime stories.",
  "about_the_game": "Straya is an Action based First Person Shooter set in Australia around the late 1960's. With a focus on surviving the many dangerous animals that inhabit the land, air and water, the player can perform jobs, hunt, collect and roam freely in an open world.<br />\r\n<br />\r\nTravel by foot, horse, chopper and boats.<br />\r\nCollect bush tucker to craft elixers.<br />\r\nUse the metal detector to find valuables and avoid land mines.<br />\r\nPan for gold and fish in the creeks and rivers.<br />\r\nGet access to special items by performing jobs and discovering locations.<br />\r\nExperience elements based on the Dreamtime stories.",
